---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Marathon Runners & Endurance Athletes"
	description="Specialist care for runners, cyclists, triathletes and endurance athletes at every level. Anti-gravity treadmill, running analysis, bike fitting, podiatry, sports massage and hydrotherapy to keep you training."
>
	<PageHero
		title="& Endurance Athletes"
		highlight="Marathon Runners"
		subtitle="Runners, cyclists, triathletes and endurance athletes at every level — from first-timers to seasoned competitors."
		breadcrumb="Marathon Runners & Endurance Athletes"
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Endurance sport"
		heading="Specialist care for the"
		highlight="long game"
		image="/sports-physio/hero-running.jpg"
		imageAlt="Runner training outdoors"
	>
		<p>Endurance sport places cumulative demands on the body that create a unique set of vulnerabilities. At Balance, we work with runners, cyclists, triathletes and endurance athletes at every level, from first-timers to seasoned competitors, providing the specialist care that keeps you moving forward.</p>
		<p>We are currently training individuals to swim the channel, climb mountains, run marathons and cycle everything from London to Brighton to L'Étape du Tour.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Keep training"
		heading="Niggles don't have to mean"
		highlight="stopping"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/antigravity.webp"
		imageAlt="Anti-gravity treadmill at Balance Physio"
	>
		<p>Preventing niggles from turning into overuse injuries is the defining challenge of endurance sport, and we understand that telling you to stop is not an option.</p>
		<p>Our anti-gravity treadmill allows you to maintain and improve your cardiovascular fitness and running form while addressing the issues causing injured tissues, so your training never has to stop completely.</p>
		<p>Running analysis and bike fitting identify any biomechanical inefficiencies that cause injury over hundreds of miles, while podiatry, sports massage and hydrotherapy keep your body recovering effectively between sessions.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Ready on race day"
		heading="Strong, balanced and"
		highlight="ready to perform"
		image="/slider-bike.webp"
		imageAlt="Cyclist on a long ride"
	>
		<p>At Balance, we understand that your race represents months of commitment and effort. Our 25-strong team works together to keep you on the road, on the bike and in the water, building towards your goal with a body that is strong, balanced and ready to perform when it counts most.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
